UpSetR wrapper for sigora results

sigora_upsetR.Rd

UpSetR wrapper for sigora results

sigora_upsetR(sigora_res, GPStable, ...)

Arguments

sigora_res

Object returned by the sigoraWrappR function
GPStable

Object returned by makeGPS_wrappR function, setting dev=TRUE
...

other parameters to upset

Examples

sigora_res <- prora::sigora_example
GPStable <- prora::GPStab

sigora_upsetR(sigora_res, GPStable)
#> Joining, by = "pathwayId"
#> Joining, by = "gene"
